000100******************************************************************        
000200**                        DSWS004                               **        
000300**                                                              **        
000400**  THIS IS A WORKING STORAGE INCLUDE FOR USE WITHIN THE        **        
000500**  RECEIVING PRINT PACKAGE SYSTEM.                             **        
000510**                                                              **        
000520**  THIS INCLUDE WILL INCLUDE VARIOUS PRINTER LINE COMMANDS     **        
000521**  TO BE SENT TO PRINTERS BASED ON THE TYPE OF PRINTER AND     **        
000522**  WHAT THE PRINTER CAN BE PROGRAMMED TO DO.                   **        
000530**                                                              **        
000700******************************************************************        
000710                                                                          
000720 01  DS004-PRINTEK-LINE-COMMANDS.                                         
000721     05  DS004-PLC-LOAD-FORM.                                             
000722         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE 'L'.           
000723*             HEX VALUE 27 D3                                             
000724         10  DS004-PLC-LF-FORM-NBR       PIC 9(1)   VALUE ZERO.           
000725         10  DS004-PLC-LF-LPI            PIC X(3).                        
000726         10  FILLER                      PIC X(126) VALUE SPACES.         
000727                                                                          
000728     05  DS004-PLC-CUT-FORM.                                              
000729         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE 'C'.           
000730*             HEX VALUE 27 C3                                             
000733         10  FILLER                      PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.         
000734                                                                          
000740     05  DS004-PLC-ACTIVATE-FF-PROC.                                      
000741         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE '^F'.           
000742*             HEX VALUE 5F C6                                             
000743         10  FILLER                      PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.         
000749                                                                          
000750     05  DS004-PLC-DEACTIVATE-FF-PROC.                                    
000751         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE '^O'.           
000752*             HEX VALUE 5F D6                                             
000753         10  FILLER                      PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.         
000754                                                                          
000755     05  DS004-PLC-DEACTIVATE-IMAGE.                                      
000756         10  FILLER                      PIC X(4)   VALUE '^PN '.         
000757*             HEX VALUE 5F D7 D5 40                                       
000758         10  DS004-PLC-DI-LPI            PIC X(3).                        
000759         10  FILLER                      PIC X(125) VALUE SPACES.         
000760                                                                          
000761*  THE FOLLOWING COMMAND ACTIVATES IMAGER MODE WITH A CARRIAGE            
000762*  RETURN (THE ^- FOLLOWING THE PY).                                      
000763                                                                          
000764     05  DS004-PLC-ACTIVATE-IMAGE1.                                       
000765         10  FILLER                      PIC X(5)   VALUE '^PY^-'.        
000766*             HEX VALUE 5F D7 D5 5F 60                                    
000767         10  FILLER                      PIC X(127) VALUE SPACES.         
000768                                                                          
000769*  THE FOLLOWING COMMAND ACTIVATES IMAGER MODE WITHOUT PERFORMING         
000770*  A CARRIAGE RETURN (THE ^- FOLLOWING THE PY IS REMOVED).                
000771                                                                          
000772     05  DS004-PLC-ACTIVATE-IMAGE2.                                       
000773         10  FILLER                      PIC X(5)   VALUE '^PY  '.        
000774*             HEX VALUE 5F D7 D5 40 40                                    
000775         10  FILLER                      PIC X(127) VALUE SPACES.         
000776                                                                          
000777*  THE FOLLOWING COMMAND IS TO BE USED IN IMAGER MODE AND IS USED         
000778*  TO PERFORM A CARRIAGE RETURN.                                          
000779                                                                          
000780     05  DS004-PLC-IMAGE-CAR-RETRN.                                       
000781         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE '^-'.           
000782*             HEX VALUE 5F 60                                             
000783         10  FILLER                      PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.         
000784                                                                          
000785*  THE FOLLOWING COMMAND IS TO BE USED IN IMAGER MODE AND IS USED         
000786*  TO PERFORM A FORM FEED.                                                
000787                                                                          
000788     05  DS004-PLC-IMAGE-FORM-FEED.                                       
000789         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE '^,'.           
000790*             HEX VALUE 5F 6B                                             
000791         10  FILLER                      PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.         
000792                                                                          
000793*  THE FOLLOWING COMMAND IS TO BE USED IN IMAGER MODE AND IS A            
000794*  GENERAL PURPOSE TERMINATING COMMAND.                                   
000795                                                                          
000796     05  DS004-PLC-IMAGE-SEQ-TERM.                                        
000797         10  FILLER                      PIC X(2)   VALUE '^G'.           
000798*             HEX VALUE 5F C7                                             
000799         10  FILLER                      PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.         
